{"tid":367250,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[Whatsapp] 澗谷 石澗/行山戶外運動group","createTime":"2017-08-20T15:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T14:36:19.000Z","uid":5780,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"028030f1f4b39105930a438b015581623113c22c","tid":367250,"uid":5780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:19:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">處暑</span>迎<span style=\"color: maroon;\">秋</span> 及時<span style=\"color: teal;\">行樂</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HOVgmYt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHOVgmYt.jpg&h=036276a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/220998/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/220998/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>前言</strong></span><br />\n行澗同行山唔同 講求反應、平衡力<br />\n要有一定<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>行山/戶外攀爬</strong></span>, <br />\n本群主要都係開石澗團、玩水為主, 識游水可以玩更加多活動<br />\n有時會有泳綑/浮潛/行山/露營團<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成員須知</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JzynyMkkPh32p9pbxUEg2tZhCJpcl8bC6r7qnk3sL8I/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1JzynyMkkPh32p9pbxUEg2tZhCJpcl8bC6r7qnk3sL8I%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=3k1Yr7EOvA77ptG9n88WTW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=94c03842\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1JzynyMkkPh32p9pbxUEg2tZhCJpcl8bC6r7qnk3sL8I/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">加入Whatsapp 群組</span></strong><br />\nGoogle drive link: <a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/fuZOc8Ly7uQOvYT63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FfuZOc8Ly7uQOvYT63&d=3k1Yr7EOvA77ptG9n88WTW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9024922b\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/fuZOc8Ly7uQOvYT63</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">群組背景 </span></strong><br />\n1. 大部分人8,90後, 連登冇女唔係新鮮事, hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 主要星期六日開團, 閒日都有機會出團<br />\n<br />\n3. 開團冇指定行邊區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">群組規則</span></strong><br />\n1. 本群成立旨在探遊山野石澗等戶外運動，每季最少出席一次行澗/山活動, 潛水者must kick。如有合理解釋(養傷/外遊/返工等), 煩請同admin講聲, 我地會酌情處理 <br />\n<br />\n2. 愛護郊野, 不破壞生態, 做個有公德心行山人士<br />\n<br />\n3. 講野串/唔識尊重/收兵/厹: 即踢, 搵食死番去8,90後交友gp<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>行石澗好處多</strong></span><br />\n1. 生命源於水, 親親大自然<br />\n<br />\n2. 訓練自己既冒險精神同埋勇氣<br />\n<br />\n3. 石澗山水交融, 風景優美<br />\n<br />\n4. 較廣闊既石澗, 可以選擇行水/石/林路, 變化萬千<br />\n<br />\n5. 夏天行石澗比較涼快<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>行澗注意事項</strong></span><br />\n1. <strong>好天先好行石澗! 好天先好行石澗! 好天先好行石澗! </strong><br />\n好重要, 所以要講三次, 石澗出意外, 好多時都係雨天地滑/山洪暴發做成 <br />\n<br />\n2. 一對防跣鞋 <br />\n想知防唔防跣, 可以係屋企個浴缸度試下 <br />\n防跣鞋亦都唔係萬能, 踩落生滿青苔既石頭, 著咩都係跣 <br />\n<br />\n3. 其他裝備 <br />\n防水袋: 以防萬一, 為貴重物品保命 <br />\n淺色衫褲: 石澗多蚊 <br />\n手套: 冇咁易比尖石割傷 <br />\n<br />\n4. 個人能力<br />\n有足夠體力攀爬、上落, 基本行山經驗 <br />\n良好既平衡力、觀察力、敏捷既身手 <br />\n如果識游水就更加好<br />\n<br />\n5. 量力而為 <br />\n唔識游水既唔好跳潭落潭 <br />\n冇能力攀上岩壁既話, 寧願行山路避險<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>過往活動精華, 未能盡錄</strong></span><br />\n<strong>九大石澗:</strong><br />\n蓮花石澗 蟠龍飛瀑:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mlJblnE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmlJblnE.jpg&h=d0a1ded4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梧桐石澗 玉女瀑:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/IPzg1CW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIPzg1CW.jpg&h=fd1eb9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大城石澗:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5fNufjD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5fNufjD.jpg&h=fc034635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n橫涌石澗:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3MVh2F1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3MVh2F1.jpg&h=0f8a236a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙鹿石澗 四疊潭:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fH1jBTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfH1jBTp.jpg&h=24e324d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬丈布 鼻涕瀑:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/i4Rf0KE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fi4Rf0KE.jpg&h=4b07fc79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屏南石澗 九疊潭之一:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/t5G3PaT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ft5G3PaT.jpg&h=aca2bfb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃龍石澗 黃龍瀑:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/aiefKbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaiefKbd.jpg&h=436e4294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昂深石澗 千層瀑:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Do6JqMN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDo6JqMN.jpg&h=27003f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>險澗之一:</strong><br />\n臥龍石澗 龍爪潭:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sZE7F49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsZE7F49.jpg&h=e595b7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東馬肚坑 撲樹崖:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eC1wshQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeC1wshQ.jpg&h=a0c18f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紫淺石澗 92:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cllDRER.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcllDRER.jpg&h=82ff261f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>出海:</strong><br />\n橋咀島浮潛:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9zRHA9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9zRHA9G.jpg&h=7a760ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OdrBqgQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOdrBqgQ.jpg&h=b413fd33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n火石洲:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/nxux67j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fnxux67j.jpg&h=a20b932f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5UMPTEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5UMPTEo.jpg&h=53b757c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ab4I3kZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAb4I3kZ.jpg&h=0203dae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/juj6FHw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fjuj6FHw.jpg&h=38d49148&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbd5a5edf05cb87cfc60dcba02fa2acbf1c75569","tid":367250,"uid":135960,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8408b720755eca245951d9ade1498300132eb902","tid":367250,"uid":35844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬 我想挽 收我ok??</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f7c758c32885a18c8bd96cf46b60b5085f21ef","tid":367250,"uid":5780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬 我想挽 收我ok??</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7316a62b00bffa0fc409976f4a2fa98843393369","tid":367250,"uid":135960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:29:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14623b376b289a462ecf5018e7c4026eb9cd752c","tid":367250,"uid":2403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬 我想挽 收我ok??</blockquote>"},{"pid":"dbfffe7684bfbc1582e974237db15d8061e54e83","tid":367250,"uid":40883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T1